{
  "stem": "24259.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing that I really recall and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Germany, they placed us in a DP camp, again DP standing for Displaced Persons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were placed with other Jewish families at a camp in Pocking, spelled-- in Germany, called P-O-K-I-N-G.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I recall, it was not very far from Munich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was within a short driving distance from Munich, so that kind of locates it where it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The D camp was formerly used as a German army base, if you will.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put everyone-- the barracks were still-- for the most part still standing, although I remember seeing rubble.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So some of them obviously were knocked down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember seeing various-- and playing with military hardware that was still there, and finding certain things like bullets and things and-- that presented themselves as good toys at the time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And each family was given a room within the barracks to live in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember just being-- having one faucet for water down the end of the hallway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like a central hallway and there were rooms to either side of the hallway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't-- there were no showers or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The sanitary facilities were in another building on the other side of a lot away from the building that I guess was shared by other barracks as well.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I do remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember my father building a small hut next to the window of our room-- the room had one window-- where he would store other things, wood.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he would also store chickens and, and, and geese and ducks and things, livestock, if you will, that they would feed and make fat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my mother would-- the rabbi would kill one, and she would cook one up occasionally and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
